        "content": "### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: standard, priority + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'standard' → Airtable · ②→ Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)",
